How all can users interact with an inspiration?
They can bookmark it to keep track of what it's used for or to easily add it to projects
They can vote on it to increase it's popularity and traction - maybe downvote to keep out spam and bad stuff
They can add it to existing projects as inspiration

Maybe:
They can add it to past projects as potential inspiration
They can suggest a project to add it to from the inspiration

How can users add an inspiration?
By uploading img/video/direct linking url
By using a browser plugin to capture something on the web page

What is required in submitting an inspiration?
Being image focused it will need either a picture or impact text
Some description of why - could be one sentence

